create table if not default.code_owners_local on cluster replicated 
 ( 
     search_key__owner  String, 
     search_key__repo   String, 
     search_key__origin String, 
     hexsha             String, 
     authored_date      DateTime64(3), 
     filepath           String, 
     module             String, 
     name               String, 
     email              String, 
     github_login       String, 
     misc               String 
 ) 
     engine = ReplicatedReplacingMergeTree('/clickhouse/tables/{shard}/code_owners', '{replica}', authored_date) 
         PARTITION BY search_key__owner 
         ORDER BY (search_key__owner, search_key__repo, hexsha) 
         SETTINGS index_granularity = 8192;
ck_create_table_ddl.distributed_table:
create table if not exists default.code_owners on cluster replicated 
 ( 
     search_key__owner  String, 
     search_key__repo   String, 
     search_key__origin String, 
     hexsha             String, 
     authored_date      DateTime64(3), 
     filepath           String, 
     module             String, 
     name               String, 
     email              String, 
     github_login       String, 
     misc               String 
 ) 
     engine = Distributed('replicated', 'default', 'code_owners_local', halfMD5(hexsha));

mysql_create_table_ddl.ddl:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS peers_average_fix_intensity_role (
id INT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT,
repo VARCHAR(100),
author_email VARCHAR(100),
average_fix_intensity FLOAT)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS contributed_repos_role (
id INT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT,
author_email VARCHAR(100),
repo_count INT)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS contribution_graph_data(
id INT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT,
cntrb_login VARCHAR(100),
repo_name VARCHAR(100),
pr_count INT,
issue_count INT,
commit_count INT ,
total_contributions INT)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS developer_roles_metrics(
id INT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT,
author_email VARCHAR(100),
total_fix_commit_count INT,
maximum_fix_commit_count INT,
repo_count INT)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS total_fix_intensity (
id INT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT,
author_email VARCHAR(100),
total_fix_intensity FLOAT)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS repo_code_metrics (id int PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT,owner varchar(255) NOT NULL,repo varchar(255) NOT NULL,created_at DateTime,sha varchar(255),nloc int,average_nloc float,average_cyclomatic_complexity float,average_token_count float)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS network_metrics (id int primary key auto_increment, repo varchar(255) not null, month varchar(255), num_nodes int, num_edges int, num_collaborations int, in_degree_centrality float, out_degree_centrality float, triangles int, transitivity float, clustering float, reciprocity float, density float, components_number int, avg_degree float)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS privilege_events
(
    search_key__owner varchar(256),
    search_key__repo varchar(256),
    actor_login varchar(64),
    added_to_project int,
    converted_note_to_issue int,
    deployed int,
    deployment_environment_changed int,
    locked int,
    merged int,
    moved_columns_in_project int,
    pinned int,
    removed_from_project int,
    review_dismissed int,
    transferred int,
    unlocked int,
    unpinned int,
    user_blocked int
)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS developer_contrib_count_metrics
(
   search_key__owner varchar(256),
   search_key__repo varchar(256),
   author_name   varchar(64),
   author_email  varchar(128),
   commit_num   int,
   line_of_code   int
)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS developer_role_network_metrics
(
   search_key__owner  varchar(256),
   search_key__repo  varchar(256),
   author_name   varchar(64),
   author_email  varchar(128),
   degree_centrality   int,
   eigenvector_centrality double
)
